---
layout: base
navigation: blog
---
%h1 Gluster Blog
%p.lead News and Announcements regarding 
%dl
  - for post in site.posts
    .post
      %h2.post-title 
        %a{:href=>post.url}= post.title
        %small
          &nbsp;
          = post.date.strftime( '%d %B %Y' )
          - if post.author
            %span.author 
              by
              %a{ :href => "#authorpage" }
                = post.author
      .article
        = post.content
